{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sisyphos uses a declarative syntax,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"so you can simply state how the user interface of your app under test should look like."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Your code is simpler and easier to read than ever before, saving you time and maintenance."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"There’s no need for manually tweaking sleeps or timeouts."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"And no need to write imperative code to wait for elements to appear."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Your tests will wait automatically exactly as long as needed to have all elements on the screen."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"As soon as the elements appear, the tests will interact with them and continue."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sisyphos builds on top of Apple’s "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/xctest\/user_interface_tests"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Therefore, no extra software or tooling is needed and the risk of breaking with new Xcode or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Swift versions is limited."}]},{"anchor":"Contributing-Bugs-and-Feature-Requests","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Contributing, Bugs, and Feature Requests"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sisyphos is an open-source project licensed under the Apache-2.0 license."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Please report any bugs or feature requests at its "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/SisyphosTests\/Sisyphos"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]